 <span data-ttu-id="9393d-348">Ad esempio, il codice Microsoft Visual c# seguente:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-348">For example, the following Microsoft Visual C# code:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
writer.Formatting = Formatting.Indented;  
writer.WriteStartElement("root");  
 writer.WriteAttributeString("xmlns","x",null,"urn:abc");  
 writer.WriteStartElement("item");  
 writer.WriteStartAttribute("href",null);  
 writer.WriteString("#");  
 writer.WriteQualifiedName("test","urn:abc");  
 writer.WriteEndAttribute();  
 writer.WriteEndElement();  
 writer.WriteEndElement();  
 writer.Close();  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9393d-349">Genera il seguente output:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-349">Generates the following output:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<root xmlns:x="urn:abc">  
 <item href="#x:test"/>  
 </root>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9393d-350">Se `ns` esegue il mapping a quello predefinito corrente, senza il prefisso viene generato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-350">If `ns` maps to the current default namespace, no prefix is generated.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9393d-351">Quando si scrivono i valori di attributo, questo metodo genera un prefisso se `ns` non viene trovato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-351">When writing attribute values, this method generates a prefix if `ns` is not found.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9393d-352">Quando si scrive il contenuto dell'elemento, genera un'eccezione se `ns` non viene trovato.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-352">When writing element content, it throws an exception if `ns` is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="9393d-353">Se questo writer supporta gli spazi dei nomi (<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Namespaces%2A> è impostata su `true`), questo metodo controlla inoltre che il nome sia valido secondo la W3C raccomandazione Namespaces in XML (http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml-names).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9393d-353">If this writer supports namespaces (<xref:System.Xml.XmlTextWriter.Namespaces%2A> is set to `true`), this method also checks that the name is valid according to the W3C Namespaces in XML recommendation (http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-xml-names).</span></span>  
  
   
  
